This is my vim configurations it uses pathogen[1]
to handle plugins found here at vim-scripts[2]

Feel free to steal of be inspired

Install
clone the repos into ~/.vim
then make links to the two config files
ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc



[1] https://github.com/tpope/vim-pathogen
[2] http://vim-scripts.org/vim/scripts.html
